Defines the installation of the emacs editor and a set of emacs packages.

@author Gunnar Wrobel <p@rdus.de>
@version 1.0
@package tool_emacs

@module os_gentoo     The os_gentoo module is required for Gentoo support.

@fact operatingsystem Allows to choose the correct actions depending
                      on the operating system
@fact keyword         The keyword for the system which is used to
                      select unstable packages

@param admin_fullname The name of the administrator.
                      (Default: 'System Administrator')
@param admin_mail     The mail address of the administrator.
                      (Default: 'root@localhost')
@param screen_dark    Adapt the emacs color scheme for a dark screen?
                      (Default: false)
